     H            Y.
     F** UTLR62C ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET SUPPLIER CODE                         *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2024.04.17                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR62C'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $SUPP  10
     F*  IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*  OUT $SUPP : 10A SUPPLIER CODE (BLANK=ERROR)
     F******************************************************
     FEDIPL44 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $SUPP  10
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $SUPP
      * GET IAF PART
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     @NONY   40
     C           @NONY     CHAINEDIPL44              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELE4FIL1    $SUPP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
